text: Aegires ochum is a species of sea slug, a nudibranch, a marine, opisthobranch gastropod mollusk in the family Aegiridae.Bouchet, P. (2013). Aegires ochum Ortea, Espinosa & Caballer, 2013. In: MolluscaBase (2017). Accessed on 2017-04-25 ==Distribution== This species was described from Pointe de La Fontaine (type locality: ), GR30, Anse Bertrand, Guadeloupe. ==References== Category:Aegiridae Category:Gastropods described in 2013
title: Aegires ochum
